# No environment variables are required for local development.
#
# When running inside GitHub Actions, the following are read from the
# Actions runtime context automatically and do not need to be set manually:
#   GITHUB_TOKEN            - injected by GitHub Actions
#   EAS_PREFLIGHT_BASE_REF  - set by action.yml from the PR base branch
#   EAS_PREFLIGHT_PR_NUMBER - set by action.yml from the PR event
